MIDWEEK CONNECTION - All Ages!||<blockquote>We want all of the family Portland Christian Center to grow in their faith, and experience true transformation.  However, you&rsquo;ll need to go beyond weekend services to do this.Whether you are a parent, senior, youth or child, we have a place for you to belong on Wednesday nights! Join us for workshops and activities the entire family will enjoy!<br /><br />We offer studies just for men, just for women, awesome youth and children's activities...even a place to drop off your baby while mom and dad learn some new parenting tricks of the trade! Additionally, we serve chef-prepared, delicious family dinners on campus for a nominal fee, so you can avoid that last-minute fast food scramble. Come and find your place to belong!</blockquote>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
